OL,3,CHow the government plans to support
OL,4,CJaguar Land Rover suppliers
OL,6,FThe business secretary Peter Kyle, is
OL,7,Fworking on a unique scheme to protect
OL,8,Fthe manufacturing jobs and skills put
OL,9,Fat risk by the calamitous cyber attack
OL,10,Fon Jaguar Land Rover.
OL,12,FSources tell me that Kyle wants to
OL,13,Fmake sure that the tens of thousands
OL,14,Fof employees at JLR's suppliers are
OL,15,Fkept working and are not sent home
OL,16,Feither temporarily or permanently as a
OL,17,Fresult of JLR's shutdown - which will
OL,18,Fcontinue at least till next month and
OL,19,Fpossibly longer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
