OL,3,CHow the government plans to support
OL,4,CJaguar Land Rover suppliers
OL,6,F"The government is very worried about
OL,7,Ferosion of the UK's skills and
OL,8,Fproductive base," said a source.
OL,10,FHe has rejected a Covid-style furlough
OL,11,Fscheme, which would see these
OL,12,Femployees paid by the government for
OL,13,Fthe period they cannot work, although
OL,14,Fthis proposal has been put to him by
OL,15,Fthe chair of the business select
OL,16,Fcommittee Liam Byrne.
