OL,3,CHow the government plans to support
OL,4,CJaguar Land Rover suppliers
OL,6,FInstead, Kyle and the business
OL,7,Fdepartment are contemplating becoming
OL,8,Fthe purchaser of parts made by these
OL,9,Fsuppliers, with the intention of then
OL,10,Fselling these components to JLR as and
OL,11,Fwhen it resumes production of high-end
OL,12,Fvehicles.
OL,14,FThe government would play the same
OL,15,Fkind of role that the Bank of England
OL,16,Fplays when banks run out of cash
OL,17,Fthrough no fault of their own: it
OL,18,Fwould be the buyer of last resort for
OL,19,Fthese component makers.
