OL,3,CHow the government plans to support
OL,4,CJaguar Land Rover suppliers
OL,6,FThe rescue will not be technically
OL,7,Feasy, though, partly because JLR is a
OL,8,Flean manufacturer and does not have
OL,9,Fsignificant spare warehouse space to
OL,10,Fstore these parts.
OL,12,FThe scheme is also predicated on the
OL,13,Funproven idea that JLR hasn't
OL,14,Fpermanently lost sales as a result of
OL,15,Fthe shutdown, that these are simply
OL,16,Fsales that have been delayed.
OL,18,FThe scale of the government's
OL,19,Fpurchases of car parts could be very
OL,20,Fsignificant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
