OL,3,CHow the government plans to support
OL,4,CJaguar Land Rover suppliers
OL,6,FBy contrast, many of JLR's suppliers
OL,7,Fare barely profitable, and have
OL,8,Falready taken one serious knock this
OL,9,Fyear, when JLR temporarily ceased
OL,10,Fproduction after America's president
OL,11,FTrump imposed crippling tariffs on US
OL,12,Fautomotive imports.
OL,14,FJLR and its suppliers are a
OL,15,Fstatistically important part of the
OL,16,FUK's manufacturing base. The latest
OL,17,Fshutdown is already having a
OL,18,Fmeasurable negative effect on the UK
OL,19,Feconomy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
