OL,6,FThe cyber attack is the most damaging
OL,7,Fin UK corporate history. The identity
OL,8,Fof the perpetrator remains unknown.
OL,10,FAlthough the Chancellor recently told
OL,11,FITV News of the threat posed by
OL,12,FRussian cyber terrorists to the online
OL,13,Fsystems of British institutions, there
OL,14,Fis no evidence that Russia was behind
OL,15,Fthe assault on JLR.
